title: 5-Year-Old-Cocaine-Spider-Man
itunes:title: 5-Year-Old-Cocaine-Spider-Man
description:
Anthony and Gregg talk about their favorite part of their careers and why Gregg isn’t home every night. Erica quizzes them about their friendship and once again, one of them knows more about the other. Anthony and Gregg dissect 300 lb. men blacking out, comedy shows being shut down, and 5-year olds doing cocaine.
